body:
{{champion:113}} starts shitting on people. Riot gets out the nerf bat. Gotta take care of the champ who has been shitting on people for 3 weeks before we get to the one that's been doing it for 3 years. They haven't even given people time to adjust to playing against a champion like her (because, by their own admission, they fucked up the jungle) and they already get the nerfs on PBE? What is really going on with the balance team? Why is it that gutting a champ and slowly building him up the trend now instead of getting it right the first time? Why push out reworks that the entire community tells you are horrible ideas (Veigar) then make your video sheepishly saying "Oh, maybe we went a little too far"? 

I never once saw a series of patches that gut Psionic Storm, then slowly build it up, then gut it again.

You're next kid {{champion:32}}

